categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A Padawan served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic during the Clone Wars.

A Force-sensitive was trained in the ways of the Force by the Jedi Order during the final decade of the Galactic Republic. During a training mission the Padawan was captured by Trandoshan slavers and taken to the hunter's moon Wasskah. around 21 BBY Once there, the Padawan was to be hunted by Trandoshan hunters and, while attempting to avoid the murders, was killed there. Kalifa, the leader of a group of Jedi Initiates hiding on the moon, later informed the newly arrived Ahsoka Tano about the Padawan's fate.
